snippet.title: Commodore 16/Plus4 - 2048 - Longplay
snippet.description:
The android classic brought to the C16 by Csabo of Legion of Doom. Released 6th April, 2014.

Note: This game has no sound (who needs sound anyway?) and unlike the original, the game ends when you reach 2048.

Grab it free here: http://plus4world.powweb.com/software/2048
